    "custom_grub_terra_features_WJqKT3": {
      "type": "custom-grub-terra-features",
      "blocks": {
        "text_V44abN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>RAISED IN USA</strong></h3><p>All our live larvae are grown in the United States. </p><h3><strong>NUTRITIOUS DIET</strong></h3><p>GrubTerra’s black soldier fly larvae are raised on a nutritious diet of vegetables, fruits, and carbohydrates, giving them a healthy, balanced diet.</p><h3><strong>SUSTAINABLY RAISED</strong></h3><p>GrubTerra’s black soldier fly larvae are raised off of food waste that would have been thrown into landfills and for every 1 pound of grubs purchased 20 pounds of waste was diverted from landfills</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_V44abN"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "GrubTerra Sustainably Produced Live Larvae ",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/POSTED_8.21.2021.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "padding_top": 40,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
    "custom_grub_terra_features_Gd8Wnq": {
      "type": "custom-grub-terra-features",
      "blocks": {
        "text_zUxAJX": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>NO PRESERVATIVES</strong></h3><p>No additives. No preservatives. 100% natural. Also great for ducks, turkeys, and other fowl, as well as wild birds and fish!</p><h3><strong>STRONGER EGGSHELLS</strong></h3><p>With 75x more calcium than mealworms, GrubTerra grubs will help your flock lay strong and consistent eggs.</p><h3><strong>HEALTHIER FEATHER PRODUCTION</strong></h3><p>GrubTerras Grubs promote stronger eggshells and help hens increase their energy levels and egg production. Grubterra Grubs are also a great supplement during molting season and in the cold winter months!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_zUxAJX"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/image_39_1.png",
        "image_position": "right",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    },
